source.name: Alberta PC Leadership Campaign Contributions
source.description: Reported contributions to Alberta Progressive Conservative Leadership Candidates Gary Mar, Alison Redford and Doug Horner as of Oct. 1, 2011. Data is not complete as candidates are expected to update their contribution lists in future. For more details about the data, go to http://bit.ly/qJjynf.
